    block the storm, Flame torrent, consume the land, Scorching bolt, strike the
    foe, Incendio hit, burn the soul, Ember shield, guard the path, Frost surge,
    spread through the realm, Frost arrow, fly to the heart, Freeze blast, hit the
    soul, Glacial wall, block the attack, Sunbeam storm, flood the area, Stellar
    shard, shoot the enemy, Radiant pulse, strike the weak, Bright barrier, block
    the fall, Nightfall storm, consume the land, Dark bolt, fly through the void,
    Shadow strike, burn the soul, Dark wall, block the storm, Hellfire storm, rage
    through the world, Fire shard, pierce the night, Blazing hit, burn the foe, Fire
    wall, stand against the attack, Snowstorm, engulf the realm, Icy bolt, fly to
    the heart, Glacial hit, freeze the enemy, Frost ward, block the fall, Gleaming
    sphere, cover all, Lumos arrow, fly through the air'
